quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,"Truly, the Day of Decision is the appointed time for all of them"
  44,41,"the Day when no friend shall be of the least avail to another, nor shall any be helped"
  44,42,"save those to whom God shows mercy. Surely, He is the Mighty, the Merciful One"
  44,43,Surely the fruit of the Zaqqum tree
  44,44,shall be food for the sinners
  44,45,"like the dregs of oil, it shall boil in their bellies"
  44,46,like the boiling of hot water
  44,47,"[A voice will cry], \"Seize him and drag him into the midst of Hell"
  44,48,Then pour boiling water over his head as punishment
  44,49,"Taste this; you who considered yourself the mighty, the honourable"
  44,50,This is what you doubted
  44,51,But those mindful of God will be in a safe place
  44,52,among gardens and springs
  44,53,"dressed in fine silk and in rich brocade, and they will face each other"
  44,54,"so it will be. We shall wed them to maidens with large, dark eyes"
  44,55,"They will call therein for every kind of fruit, in peace and security"
  44,56,"They will not taste death therein, save the first death. God will save them from the torment of Hell"
  44,57,as an act of grace. That will be the supreme triumph
  44,58,"We have made this Quran easy to understand, in your own language, so that they may take heed"
  44,59,Wait then; they too are waiting